{"tid":683281,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟長期肚有氣，朝早痾潺，左腰頂住頂住，左後腰會痛，醫生問︰你擔心乜野？","createTime":"2018-05-29T14:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T23:01:14.000Z","uid":54684,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"665c62cc9a49ed885ae0e62c1ce4628b376c3876","tid":683281,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"話說小弟長期肚多氣體，都成6~7年了，出來做野1~2年就開始咁<br />\n<br />\n會痾潺，綠綠啡啡色，往往加埋朝早屙氣<br />\n其餘整日都無乜，係夜晚有極低機會再有一次<br />\n<br />\n黃昏排便最正常<br />\n但有時左腰/左後腰都會頂住頂住<br />\n往往要左手幫手撳下撳下個肚  會有時幫到排出谷住既氣<br />\n排左會有舒緩作用<br />\n<br />\n以往都睇左好幾次公立醫生街症<br />\n食化胃氣丸，無效<br />\n留大便check，一切正常<br />\n留大便 + 抽血check，一切正常<br />\n<br />\n前排左後腰會輕輕痛   排便有助舒緩<br />\n於是排多次街症  又問醫生使唔使check下  會痛喎<br />\n醫生一臉不耐煩問︰你擔心乜野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後畀左3個樽仔個留便算    打發我走<br />\n<br />\n我係咪唔使理住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd9e2449c95df0b2a551ce5eb7873d3fb94ffdc","tid":683281,"uid":79974,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況梗係睇中醫啦"},{"pid":"21e3e987c77703e56b99d4ba3db49bfe6efed9da","tid":683281,"uid":61271,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:44:44.000Z","msg":"醫生問你擔心乜野係一種溝通技巧<br />\n<br />\n因為當你所有檢查都正常，醫生就要知你有無咩諗法或者想醫生點樣幫<br />\n<br />\n例如你可能話好驚生cancer ，咁佢就會解釋比你聽點解唔似<br />\n<br />\n又或者你話好想照腸鏡胃鏡，咁佢可能會作安排或轉介"},{"pid":"c496cdfed17dabd21592f5830484aad6617bdbab","tid":683281,"uid":132653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:55:24.000Z","msg":"會唔會壓力太大 精神緊張"},{"pid":"bfe0fd1cfbb00e800ecd1e2ecfeb51dbea6f832d","tid":683281,"uid":105888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:58:51.000Z","msg":"有冇照過？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能有膽石"},{"pid":"e751dc29c8f0e8f113aa1e95d42f77c8dab1e0f1","tid":683281,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:09:32.000Z","msg":"咁你擔心乜嘢吖？<br />\n醫生問你你問到佢講囉"},{"pid":"ea17619931f4a3567c80dee1332be08175da3934","tid":683281,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfe0fd1cfbb00e800ecd1e2ecfeb51dbea6f832d","tid":683281,"uid":105888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:58:51.000Z","msg":"有冇照過？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能有膽石"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:12:02.000Z","msg":"腰係腎石<br />\n<br />\n利申：有病史，但肯定樓主冇<br />\n如果生腎石放兩個屁就搞掂就好"},{"pid":"44cceded9bd61a9628ca6083611494c0b6398c32","tid":683281,"uid":49153,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:19:51.000Z","msg":"胃氣撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時已經多胃氣<br />\n以前上堂趴係枱面瞓<br />\n一起身會有勁多胃氣<br />\ngur足幾秒 有時成十秒先gur完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每幾個月/大半年會有一次勁多胃氣/腸氣<br />\n個肚會間歇性咁痛 一痛起上黎都幾痛下<br />\n<br />\n唔知係我特別 定其他人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d2f272bbe1965868437283b918b4dc3f9c76b7","tid":683281,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:43:20.000Z","msg":"去私家醫院睇啦"},{"pid":"9b394d4f1ce73249edb8b166d6f703636b585d7d","tid":683281,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:44:55.000Z","msg":"戒食紅肉、煎炸、生冷野<br />\n減少食豆類<br />\n多食蔬果<br />\n做運動"},{"pid":"c3aed0da909292331ad8b3362c7c5aa536065869","tid":683281,"uid":34939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:50:59.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過腸道菌種唔平衝<br />\n試下食益生菌?"},{"pid":"bb2fabfb6e487544d67813839ddbc51864edde1a","tid":683281,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:54:17.000Z","msg":"呢啲問題睇中醫啦"},{"pid":"5049f871e18b48c09bb453bdd91978e563c2f7b7","tid":683281,"uid":68098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:54:22.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪長期飲奶茶？"},{"pid":"6a7b3189049a9a8d1d080e17542ed783aba6cf5e","tid":683281,"uid":54455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:56:31.000Z","msg":"番工生活忙易有肚脹"},{"pid":"b01799af4d0a4cc320af5431177c0579cf7ae27e","tid":683281,"uid":120123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:58:35.000Z","msg":"Symptoms<br />\nThe signs and symptoms of IBS vary. The most common include:<br />\n<br />\nAbdominal pain, cramping or bloating that is typically relieved or partially relieved by passing a bowel movement<br />\nExcess gas<br />\nDiarrhea or constipation &mdash; sometimes alternating bouts of diarrhea and constipation<br />\nMucus in the stool<br />\nMost people with IBS experience times when the signs and symptoms are worse and times when they improve or even disappear completely ?"},{"pid":"17af8af95efea2f3b79baa4dff3fa2730c9a94a8","tid":683281,"uid":1022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胃氣撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時已經多胃氣<br />\n以前上堂趴係枱面瞓<br />\n一起身會有勁多胃氣<br />\ngur足幾秒 有時成十秒先gur完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每幾個月/大半年會有一次勁多胃氣/腸氣<br />\n個肚會間歇性咁痛 一痛起上黎都幾痛下<br />\n<br />\n唔知係我特別 定其他人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n趴係檯訓有胃氣係正常"},{"pid":"3e7ae79ac8294675cd79d84d705cf094c6583ecd","tid":683281,"uid":132676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"借post分享下<br />\n已經因為胃氣問題三個月冇正常食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有日搭搭下車反胃以為暈車浪, 點知至此就一直都好多胃氣, 胃口又差, 三餐變半餐, 飯唔一定吞到所以好多時都食麵<br />\n<br />\n睇過西醫驗過血, 醫生都搵唔到原因<br />\n睇中醫就話胃炎, 但咁耐都未好返應該仲有其他問題, 另外最近再有睇中醫調理身體, 希望有用<br />\n<br />\n壓力方面, 主要壓力係來自擔心食唔食到嘢, 唔敢出街食因為驚食一啖就食唔落, 明明好肚餓但一發作就會即刻想嘔, 都唔會叫屋企人煮飯我食, 驚哂咗佢哋一番心機, 唔知點先可以好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48211c668b2766f16f8e68a34e0d07fdb9047bd","tid":683281,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cb78e752274067343ae9b27be9ced146c451340","tid":683281,"uid":57848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"你食啲咩又唔講，生活習慣又唔講，淨係屌咗醫生唔耐煩，我回你post都唔耐煩啦"},{"pid":"ad494f874d13aeafa175fbb2ba004d3e5311cab2","tid":683281,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"睇完你描述，你根本冇事，醫生覺得你煩好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我都係咁四圍睇醫生，但根本冇事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n挑選食物小心啲囉，明顯有某啲食物唔岩你食"},{"pid":"b06556f21e6ec6bb229ab04d2a9559421cdc6b01","tid":683281,"uid":183453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"食清淡啲戒奶茶咖啡<br />\n戒奶 有機會你身體分解唔到乳糖 導致脹氣<br />\n睇下自己係咪鼻敏感長期鼻塞<br />\n因為長時間用口呼吸都有機會吸左啲氣入個位胃度<br />\n食完野都可以按摩下中腹幫助消化"},{"pid":"e06e4acef6068999d8924b2fe75becb47e451289","tid":683281,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"醫生一眼睇穿你情緒有問題"},{"pid":"dcfddf4f1c4e957fb5e8825ee37793044ed089c3","tid":683281,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e7ae79ac8294675cd79d84d705cf094c6583ecd","tid":683281,"uid":132676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"借post分享下<br />\n已經因為胃氣問題三個月冇正常食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有日搭搭下車反胃以為暈車浪, 點知至此就一直都好多胃氣, 胃口又差, 三餐變半餐, 飯唔一定吞到所以好多時都食麵<br />\n<br />\n睇過西醫驗過血, 醫生都搵唔到原因<br />\n睇中醫就話胃炎, 但咁耐都未好返應該仲有其他問題, 另外最近再有睇中醫調理身體, 希望有用<br />\n<br />\n壓力方面, 主要壓力係來自擔心食唔食到嘢, 唔敢出街食因為驚食一啖就食唔落, 明明好肚餓但一發作就會即刻想嘔, 都唔會叫屋企人煮飯我食, 驚哂咗佢哋一番心機, 唔知點先可以好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"same 做下運動會好少少"},{"pid":"5dcaf0fc21e03a4912d4e773f8b6650ecedbf823","tid":683281,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"咁既問題都唔算問題？...犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ca577c5e1a6690eb7072a96eb4945ad493e8a0","tid":683281,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06556f21e6ec6bb229ab04d2a9559421cdc6b01","tid":683281,"uid":183453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"食清淡啲戒奶茶咖啡<br />\n戒奶 有機會你身體分解唔到乳糖 導致脹氣<br />\n睇下自己係咪鼻敏感長期鼻塞<br />\n因為長時間用口呼吸都有機會吸左啲氣入個位胃度<br />\n食完野都可以按摩下中腹幫助消化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"多謝   我研究下"}]}